front.title: •I'll Try Spinning
front.gametext: Landed starfighters and vehicles aboard starships are forfeit = 0. Once during your control phase may target your N-1 starfighter and opponent's starfighter present at same system. Both players draw destiny. You add your starfighter's power and maneuver. Opponent adds starfighter's power. Starship with lowest total is lost.

counterpart: The Deflector Shield Is Too Strong
